## Claude Code

### Option 1: CLI (Recommended)
```bash
claude mcp add knowledge-mcp -- knowledge-mcp
```

### Option 2: Project-level (.mcp.json)
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "knowledge-mcp": {
      "command": "/path/to/knowledge-mcp",
      "args": ["--data-path", ".knowledge"]
    }
  }
}
```

### Option 3: Global (~/.claude/settings.json)
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "knowledge-mcp": {
      "command": "/path/to/knowledge-mcp",
      "args": []
    }
  }
}
```

## Gemini

Edit `~/.gemini/settings.json`:
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "knowledge-mcp": {
      "command": "/path/to/knowledge-mcp",
      "args": ["--data-path", "/path/to/.knowledge"]
    }
  }
}
```

## System Prompt Integration

Append contents of `SYSTEM_PROMPT.md` to your assistant's config file (`~/.claude/CLAUDE.md`, `~/.gemini/GEMINI.md`, etc.) to ensure automatic knowledge retrieval and updates.
